cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper discusses a framework for policy evaluation in reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The use of the extended Kalman filter and the optimization method proposed in the paper are relevant to these sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.NE.
